---
---

<section class="bg-tertiary text-on-tertiary relative overflow-hidden">
  <!-- Subtle tech pattern overlay -->
  <div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-10">
    <div class="absolute inset-0" style="background-image: url('/pattern.svg'); background-repeat: repeat;"></div>
  </div>

  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8 py-20 lg:py-32 relative z-10">
    <!-- Label -->
    <div class="mb-6">
      <span class="font-sans text-xs tracking-[0.2em] text-secondary-fixed-dim uppercase">Engineering the Next Paradigm</span>
    </div>

    <!-- Main Headline -->
    <h1 class="font-serif text-5xl md:text-6xl lg:text-7xl text-white leading-[0.9] font-black tracking-tighter mb-12 ink-bleed">
      The Digital
      <br />
      Infrastructure
      <br />
      of <span class="italic text-secondary-fixed-dim">Tomorrow.</span>
    </h1>

    <!-- CTA Button -->
    <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-8 items-start">
      <a
        href="/contact"
        class="bg-secondary-fixed text-on-secondary-fixed px-10 py-5 font-sans font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-sm hover:bg-white transition-all duration-300 flex items-center gap-4 group"
      >
        Start Your Transformation
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-4 w-4 group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3" />
        </svg>
      </a>
      <p class="max-w-md text-secondary-fixed-dim text-lg font-body leading-relaxed border-l border-secondary-fixed-dim/30 pl-6">
        We don't sell tools — we engineer outcomes. Strategy, architecture, and precision-built
        systems that last. No hype. No vendor lock-in. Just results that compound.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
